| url = https://archive.org/details/organobismuthche00suzu
| author1 = Hitomi Suzuki
| author2 = Yoshihiro Matano
| publisher = Elsevier
| year = 2001
| isbn = 0-444-20528-4
| pages = [https://archive.org/details/organobismuthche00suzu/page/n419 403]–404
}}</ref>

==安全性==
氯化铋有毒，能刺激胃肠道和呼吸道，与皮肤接触可能导致灼伤。

